	section("3️⃣  FOOD FIGHT", "Throw food at other players to raise their Cleanliness. Last Chef Standing earns the Golden Apron. Cooked dishes hit much harder than raw ingredients.", C.warn)
	section("🧼  CLEANLINESS", "Your health bar. Enemies raise it by hitting you with food. Hit 100% and you drop everything in a full-blown grocery disaster.", blue)
